NAME
    Test::Time - Override time() and sleep() core function for tests.

SYNOPSIS
      use Test::Time; # just use

      time(); # fixed time

      sleep 1; # increment internal time (return immediately)
      time(); # incremented

DESCRIPTION
    Test::Time is for tests around time. You just use this module and your
    tests are all "time safe".

AUTHOR
